snippet.textDisplay: Well done Zoheb bhai once again. This is one of my favorites from the songs you and Nazia sung. I hope you remember me, I served your dad, Syed Baseer Hassan when he had brain hemorrhage and Dr. Nadir Ali treated him in Aga Khan. Loved your song. Maybe you don't know, I used to sing this song very well whenever I got a chance to sing in college and other social events in Karachi Adventist Hospital.
